        "TileImage": "$($repository 4038aa7a-f980-4231-a0b0-60d4b197d6c3).Image",
        "Description": "Three infamous hackers have arrived in mendoza today to work their way into the wineries&apos; rich database of high-end customers located deep within the mansion. One of them has already found a suitable disguise and waiting on the two others to find the perfect time to strike. Two of the targets are alone and unmoving, while one is in a crowded party climbing the social ladder. This should be an easy one, 47. Make it quick.",
